ile it wasnt horrible to sit in it just wasnt as nice as sitting in PU leather.";i:11;s:121:"The PU leather doesnt get too hot for me but my office is also typically on the cooler side in terms of room temperature.";i:12;s:71:"The leather covering the back of the chair seems to be equally durable.";i:13;s:118:"Ive accidentally scuffed the chair in a few doorways or against other hard surfaces and never noticed it leave a mark.";i:14;s:147:"Listed at PHP23990 on Lazada the Secretlab Omega 2020 Series is premium-priced reflecting the top-notch build and materials quality of the product.";i:15;s:128:"Backed by a 3-year international manufacturer warranty extendable to 5-years you should think of this as a long-term investment.";i:16;s:43:"After all youd probably spend more time in.";i:17;s:102:"As a final touch all the 2020 Omega series of gaming chairs now come with two memory foam accessories.";i:18;s:66:"That includes a headrest with a strap and a formed lumbar cushion.";i:19;s:86:"Both can be removed if you like but I found the chair much more comfortable with them.";i:20;s:78:"Usually with a gaming chair review wed show you a few photos and mention what.";i:21;s:102:"The Secretlab OMEGA 2020 Series PRIME PU Leather Gaming Chair is one of the best gaming chairs around.";i:22;s:43:"Not only is it considered an amazing chair.";i:23;s:126:"The 2020 Series Omega reviewed here still makes for an incredibly comfortable seating experience with plenty of customization.";i:24;s:48:"Lifetime license for 16 monthly plans at 1 more.";i:25;s:77:"The GT Omega Racing Chair is relatively difficult to get a hold of in the US.";i:26;s:49:"So when its available you better snag it up ASAP.";i:27;s:98:"However there are some outside sellers that will ship to US youll just have to pay a little extra.";i:28;s:52:"Its a great chair it has really good durability and.";i:29;s:91:"The Omega comes in a variety of accent colors and is currently priced at a competitive 359.";i:30;s:95:"It definitely isnt the cheapest gaming chair around but its quality rivals that of chairs weve.";i:31;s:57:"Comfort is where the GT Omega SPORT series really shines.";i:32;s:51:"Firstly it is considerably wider than my old chair.";i:33;s:88:"With my old chair it also had bucket seats the edges of the seat would dig into my back.";i:34;s:28:"In reality I got used to it.";i:35;s:106:"However after having sat in the SPORT series I realised just how much of a difference a wider chair makes.";i:36;s:70:"GT Omega Pro Gaming Office Chair - First Impressions Review - YouTube.";i:37;s:136:"My coworkers admire my chair during video calls whilst I sit there in ultimate comfort and relief knowing my back is being looked after.";i:38;s:58:"This chair is perfect for gamers and office workers alike.";i:39;s:88:"Of course it wouldnt be a massage chair if all it did was recline in a certain position.";i:40;s:79:"That would also make this Omega Serenity Massage Chair review incredibly short.";i:41;s:100:"No the chair despite its stripped-down nature does include a fair few of its own massaging features.";i:42;s:49:"Even the packaging the chair comes in is amazing.";i:43;s:116:"We ordered 2 chairs and both were very easy to build the instructions are clear and the tools to build are provided.";i:44;s:110:"The chairs look fantastic theyre very comfortable with lots of adjustments to make them just right for anyone.";i:45;s:62:"I expected something special and I have not been disappointed.";i:46;s:148:"The Secretlab Omega SoftWeave gaming chairs firm foam takes some getting used to but theres a lot to love about this highly adjustable fabric chair.";i:47;s:116:"The GT Omega Element is the gaming chair equivalent of a freshly tailored suit built to make you look and feel good.";i:48;s:28:"Build quality and materials.";i:49;s:49:"Even the packaging the chair comes in is amazing.";i:50;s:116:"We ordered 2 chairs and both were very easy to build the instructions are clear and the tools to build are provided.";i:51;s:110:"The chairs look fantastic theyre very comfortable with lots of adjustments to make them just right for anyone.";i:52;s:62:"I expected something special and I have not been disappointed.";i:53;s:83:"This is the kind of chair you can pass onto your kids as long as its taken care of.";i:54;s:124:"Just like the vintage jackets that never go out of style or seam the Secretlab chair was created with a passion for quality.";i:55;s:31:"It could be your forever chair.";i:56;s:40:"OMEGA Dark Knight 2020 Series Secretlab.";i:57;s:11:"5 out of 5.";}}